trans-unit.source: Configures ASP.NET profiles that determine how health-monitoring events are sent to event providers.
trans-unit.target: 設定 ASP.NET 設定檔，以決定如何健全狀況監視的事件傳送至事件提供者。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
This class corresponds to the `<healthMonitoring>` configuration file element.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別會對應到`<healthMonitoring>`組態檔元素。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Medium trust or higher is required to raise an event.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 中度信任或更高版本，才可引發事件。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection"></xref> class using default settings.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection"></xref>類別使用預設設定。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式不是直接從您的程式碼使用。

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the default settings that are used for this constructor.
trans-unit.target: 下表顯示使用這個建構函式的預設設定。

trans-unit.source: |Setting|Default value| |-------------|-------------------| |<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Enabled%2A>|`true`|
Gets a collection of objects that specify the settings for the buffer modes.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定的緩衝模式設定的物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: This is a collection of <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings> objects that define the manner in which health-monitoring events can be buffered before they are raised.
trans-unit.target: 這是集合的<xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings>物件定義中的健全狀況監視的事件可以緩衝處理之前會引發的方式。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings>

trans-unit.source: This property defaults to an empty <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection> collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings"></xref> objects.
Gets or sets a value indicating whether health monitoring is enabled.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值，指出是否啟用健全狀況監視。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if health monitoring is enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果啟用健全狀況監視。否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 預設值是<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.EventMappingSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.EventMappingSettings"></xref> objects.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.EventMappingSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.EventMappingSettings"></xref> objects.
The default is an empty <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.EventMappingSettingsCollection"></xref> collection.
Gets or sets the interval used by the application domain when it raises the <xref href="System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定應用程式定義域時，便會產生使用間隔<xref href="System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent"></xref>事件。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.TimeSpan> value is zero ticks, no <xref:System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.TimeSpan>值不是零次滴答聲，<xref:System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent>就會引發事件。</xref:System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent> </xref:System.TimeSpan>

trans-unit.source: The interval used by the application domain when it raises the <xref href="System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: 使用應用程式定義域時，便會產生的間隔<xref href="System.Web.Management.WebHeartbeatEvent"></xref>事件。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSettings"></xref> objects.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSettings"></xref> objects.
The default is an empty <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSettingsCollection"></xref> collection.
To be added.
Gets a <xref href="System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Configuration.ProviderSettings"></xref> objects.
The Providers property specifies which provider is used for which of the events defined in the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 提供者屬性會指定哪一個提供者使用的定義中之事件的<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection"></xref> collection.
The default is an empty <xref href="System.Configuration.ProviderSettingsCollection"></xref> collection.
Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettingsCollection"></xref> collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettings"></xref> objects.

Each <xref:System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettings> object defines a connection between an event defined in the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A> property and an event provider defined in the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Providers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 每個<xref:System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettings>物件定義中定義的事件之間的連線<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A>屬性和事件提供者中定義<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Providers%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Providers%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.EventMappings%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettings>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettingsCollection"></xref> collection.
The default is an empty <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.RuleSettingsCollection"></xref> collection
